[[File:Roewe Ei5 003.jpg|thumb|left|Roewe Ei5 station wagon rear view]]
The '''Roewe i5''' is a [[Compact car|compact]] sedan and station wagon produced by [[Roewe]].<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=https://carnewschina.com/roewe-i5-classy-compact-sedan-from-china/ |title=The Roewe i5 Is A Classy Compact Sedan From China |author=Tycho de Feijter |date=21 June 2018 |access-date=2018-08-19}}</ref> First introduced via the electric version station wagon, the '''Roewe Ei5''', the compact station wagon debuted on the 2017 Guangzhou Auto Show. The engines for the i5 is the same as the ones available in the Excelle GX. <ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=https://carnewschina.com/2018/03/01/roewe-ei5-electric-compact-wagon-ready-china/ |title=The Roewe Ei5 Electric Compact Wagon Is Ready For China |author=W.E. Ning |date=1 March 2018 |access-date=2018-08-19}}</ref>

==Roewe Ei5==
The '''Roewe Ei5''' is the electric version of the Roewe i5. Debuting during the 2017 Guangzhou Auto Show, the pricing of the Roewe Ei5 ranges from 213,800 yuan to 223,800 yuan. The power of the Ei5 comes from a single electric motor with 116 hp with a range of 300 kilometers and a 145 km/h top speed.<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=https://carnewschina.com/2017/11/17/roewe-ei5-electric-buick-another-name-body/ |title=The Roewe Ei5 Is An Electric Buick With Another Name And Body |author=Tycho de Feijter |date=17 November 2017 |access-date=2018-08-19}}</ref>

